 a^n-b^n = (a-b)(a^{n-1} + a^{n-2}b + \ldots + b^{n-1}) 
\begin{align} &(a-b)(a^{n-1} + a^{n-2}b + \ldots + b^{n-1}) \\\\ &=a^{n} + a^{n-1}b + a^{n-2}b^2 + \ldots + ab^{n-1}\\\\ &\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;- ba^{n-1} - b^2a^{n-2}-\ldots -b^{n-1}a - b^n\\\\ &=a^n-b^n \end{align}
